OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear start to the night. However, low
OL,7,Fcloud and mist will gradually move
OL,8,Finto Cornwall and west Devon, and
OL,9,Fcould bring some spots of drizzle.
OL,10,FStaying very mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FLow cloud in the west will
OL,13,Fgradually become confined to coasts
OL,14,Fduring the day, allowing warm sunny
OL,15,Fspells to develop elsewhere. The best
OL,16,Fof the sunshine likely in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
